                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thrust"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>. Karakter ini menerima <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Stealth</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Stealth</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>Karakter yang terpengaruh menerima -1 poin DMG dan mengakibatkan +1 poin DMG.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/2fc519b5fd90708c67fd63a2da75d2d6_6587096700999343703.png",
